---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="bg-[#FFFBFB] px-6 py-16 lg:px-8">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
      <span class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-[#2D2D2D] uppercase italic">
        L'Art des Ongles<span class="text-[#E29595] font-normal not-italic">.</span>
      </span>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-md text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#2D2D2D]/60">
        Onde a beleza encontra a arte e o cuidado encontra o luxo. Sua boutique de bem-estar para mãos e pés.
      </p>
      
      <div class="mt-10 flex gap-8 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#2D2D2D]/40">
        <a href="#servicos" class="hover:text-[#E29595] transition-colors">Serviços</a>
        <a href="#galeria" class="hover:text-[#E29595] transition-colors">Portfolio</a>
        <a href="#contato" class="hover:text-[#E29595] transition-colors">Agendamento</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-12 flex gap-6">
        <a href="#" class="h-10 w-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-[#2D2D2D]/5 text-[#2D2D2D]/30 hover:text-[#E29595] hover:border-[#E29595] transition-all">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"></rect><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"></path><line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"></line></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <p class="mt-16 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#2D2D2D]/30">
        © {currentYear} L'Art des Ongles. Rua das Flores, 123 - Jardins, SP.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
